"content": "<p>Frank: If you'd cleaned the wound with water or covered it with napkins, it could've introduced different types of infections to the wound.</p>",
"height": 161.0,
"outputs": ["a491a8bb-d7e5-4b61-a845-9284c9b711e8"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
