"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["894c2a71-952e-45c9-b55a-340794307a1d"],
"content": "<p>You: \"My friend dropped a knife on his foot at his home. I’m with him and wrapped it temporarily, but it needs medical attention.\"</p>",
