"components": ["ad3d9699-c9ea-4bc0-aa9f-e9656ca0791c"],
"content": "<p>You enter your friend's house. You pour yourself a glass of water. Frank goes back to a cutting board, with various vegetables chopped up on the side. There are several knives hanging above the stove.</p>",
