"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["ad3d9699-c9ea-4bc0-aa9f-e9656ca0791c"],
"content": "<p>Frank: A vegetable soup. I feel like I haven't been eating enough vegetables.</p>",
"height": 321.0,
"outputs": ["9b7812a5-cdfa-455a-b4ac-3dcae78e3fe5"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 7440.0,
"y": 10480.0
},
"95f3587c-a200-4d83-81d3-cb031c1b82b9": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["ad3d9699-c9ea-4bc0-aa9f-e9656ca0791c"],
"content": "<p>Frank: Well, I did a lot more cooking back in high school, but I've been just getting fast food a lot for the past year. The freshman dorm didn't have any convenient stove, anyhow.</p>",
"height": 402.0,
"outputs": ["e066ceb6-44a5-428e-90b7-cecd562444ad"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 322.0,
"x": 7620.0,
"y": 10900.0
},
"962d91ed-0391-4eb6-85b9-75a9cb1c7903": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": true,
"components": ["647349ca-9ebb-4d5f-b81e-500761ec1c5a", "f48f8f8e-9c8c-4bd2-b94f-0228e5832974"],
"content": "<p>Frank: More sterile than the napkins, at any rate.</p>",
"height": 313.0,
"outputs": ["50a20ddc-0a6e-4167-a492-82263b536bd3"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
