},
"9bcd7db2-fb3e-4d42-bd6a-5562d25a42ba": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": true,
"components": ["647349ca-9ebb-4d5f-b81e-500761ec1c5a"],
"content": "<p>Frank: I mean, I have a knife in my foot, but… I need to relax. Don’t want to go into shock or anything.</p>",
"height": 140.0,
"outputs": ["157ca548-e4e1-4ac6-87d6-749428776442"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 9980.0,
"y": 9780.0
},
"9ea70bad-8602-4b25-aad4-f0f9ca3f231d": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p>You: What should I do?</p>",
"height": 361.0,
"outputs": ["c5a85a61-1147-4514-8a19-5c0d8b10aba0"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 13180.0,
"y": 12780.0
},
"a2269b29-e0d1-42c8-9b76-67060018ed14": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": true,
"components": ["647349ca-9ebb-4d5f-b81e-500761ec1c5a"],
"content": "<p>Frank: Can you, um, bring a chair over? </p>",
"height": 121.0,
"outputs": ["5d06bab1-d846-495a-aeda-7b9af9aba459"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 11740.0,
"y": 10160.0
},
"aa31e639-f2e6-4cec-aad6-bd3ca242e92e": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "8bfe7259-406b-4c69-8bd6-f6d566686dec"
}
},
"autoHeight": true,
"components": [],
"content": "<p>You investigate the knife wound. It’s fully through the foot. Blood is coming out of the top and on the floor underneath.</p>",
"height": 355.0,
"outputs": ["9a28d341-e45b-4a31-b5dd-75ac4a548eb4"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 10400.0,
