"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["894c2a71-952e-45c9-b55a-340794307a1d"],
"content": "<p>911-Operator: \"When calling for help, please provide important details, so I can properly assess your situation. What’s the injury, specifically?\"</p>",
"height": 421.0,
"outputs": ["6ab68936-cb58-4370-b19c-4b6d055eb8f9"],
"theme": "orange",
"title": null,
"width": 281.0,
"x": 9660.0,
"y": 13060.0
},
"abb0f32e-b35f-4271-b631-5f0860fddd42": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": true,
"components": [],
"content": "<p>Your best friend is Frank, a guy you met in freshman year at a chess club. You're majoring in different things, so you don't see each other very often. Today, he's invited you to his house for lunch.</p>",
"height": 296.0,
"outputs": ["4ab6a842-4a58-4144-babb-fe76bee42ae0"],
"theme": "cyan",
"title": null,
"width": 321.0,
"x": 6300.0,
"y": 11140.0
},
