"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["894c2a71-952e-45c9-b55a-340794307a1d"],
"content": "<p>You: \"My friend’s foot is bleeding even though I wrapped it. Please send help!!\"</p>",
"height": 421.0,
