"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": true,
"components": ["ad3d9699-c9ea-4bc0-aa9f-e9656ca0791c"],
"content": "<p>Frank<strong>: </strong>Oh, hello there! Come on in! I was almost done making the food.</p>",
